platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Double Fines riveting point-and-click adventure thrusts players into a timeless blend of whimsical sci-fi and dark fairy tale. Clever writing and stylish visuals keep its intersecting stories appealingand at times, wickedly funnywith characters youll quickly become attached to (voiced by Elijah Wood, Jack Black, and other popular actors). Initially available with Act 1 only, Broken Age now includes the complete gamea one-of-a-kind odyssey thats full of memorable moments.
